  <h2>Notes</h2>
  <p>
    Authors emphasize the utility of LMIR as a dust-insensitive luminosity indicator when combined with BEL widths for virial MBH estimates. The catalog is positioned as a reference for upcoming wide-area IR surveys (e.g., SPHEREx) and for studies connecting AGN accretion to host and environment in the NEP-Wide field.
  </p>

